snippet: The pilot of one of the planes, both F-18 Hornets, was rescued, the Defense Department said.
abstract: Two Navy fighter jets crash into the Pacific Ocean; pilot of one of the planes, both F-18 Hornets, is rescued and taken back to the carrier Carl Vinson to receive medical attention; search and rescue teams are still looking for the pilot of the second plane.
